item.title: MySQL Workbench 8.0 点击Server Status面板Could not acquire management access for administration报错问题解决
item.description: Win10安装MySQL Workbench 8.0后连接MySQL服务器后，点击Server Status状态面板报错， 错误如下： Could not acquire management access for administration TRuntimeError: Target host is configured as Windows, but seems to be a different OS. Please review the connection settings. 解决方法： 是因为windows中文桌面
